To use this overlay:

1) Add https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sjkingo-archive/gentoo-overlay/master/overlay.xml
   to your list of overlay definitions files in /etc/layman/layman.cfg.
   It should resemble this:

     overlays  : http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/overlays/layman-global.txt
                 https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sjkingo-archive/gentoo-overlay/master/overlay.xml

2) Tell layman to resync its overlay lists, and then fetch the sjkwi overlay:

     layman -L
     layman -a sjkwi

3) Profit!
